NK050(wi)002:1: // nges don snying po'i gnad mdor bsdus pa'i sa bcad /
NK050(wi)002:3: 'dir nges don snying po'i gnad mdor bsdus pa rin po che'i sgron me 'chad pa la don gsum /
NK050(wi)002:10: mchod par brjod cing rtsom par dam bca' ba dang gsum las /
NK050(wi)002:11: dang po nges don snying po'i sogs /
NK050(wi)002:15: sems kyi rang bzhin sogs so //
NK050(wi)002:19: mthar phyin 'bras bu bstan pa dang gsum las /
NK050(wi)002:23: sems dang ye shes kyi dbye ba /
NK050(wi)002:24: 'khrul dus kyang rang bzhin 'od gsal dag pa'i chos nyid ji ltar bzhugs tshul lo //
NK050(wi)002:28: 'di'i rang rtsal phyir g.yos pa'i tshe sogs /
NK050(wi)002:31: gcig tha dad la brtag pa gnyis /
NK050(wi)002:33: des na sems rnam shes tshogs brgyad sogs /
NK050(wi)002:35: gzhan yang dgongs pa nges 'grel sogs /
NK050(wi)002:37: rang bzhin dag pa'i chos nyid ji ltar bzhugs pa'i tshul /
NK050(wi)002:38: de la zag med kyi yon tan rnams ji ltar brten pa /
NK050(wi)002:39: de dag mdo sngags kyi dgongs pa mthun par sbyar te rgyas par bshad pa dang gsum las /
NK050(wi)002:41: chos nyid ye nas dag pa'i tshul /
NK050(wi)002:42: de la glo bur gyi dri ma ji ltar brten pa /
NK050(wi)002:43: de rnams kyi don bsdus te spros pa gcod tshul lo //
NK050(wi)002:49: de la 'khor chos las dang nyon mongs sogs /
NK050(wi)002:54: zag med kyi yon tan brten tshul spyir bstan pa dang /
NK050(wi)002:55: bye brag sems nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas su bstan pa gnyis las dang po /
NK050(wi)002:56: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos sogs /
NK050(wi)002:58: mdor na 'phags pa 'da' ka ye shes sogs /
NK050(wi)002:60: mdo nas ji ltar gsungs pa /
NK050(wi)002:61: de nyid sngags dang mtshams sbyor tshul /
NK050(wi)002:62: theg chen bla med kyi rigs khams ngos bzung ba /
NK050(wi)002:63: bden gnyis kyi rnam dbye bstan pa'o //
NK050(wi)002:65: bka' 'khor gsum du ji ltar bstan tshul gyi dbye ba /
NK050(wi)002:66: de'i go rim dang drang nges kyi dbye bsal /
NK050(wi)002:67: de la gzhan gyi log rtog bzlog pa dang gsum las /
NK050(wi)002:69: 'khor lo dang po nas snying po'i rang bzhin dngos su ma bstan pa'i tshul /
NK050(wi)002:70: bar par ngo bo stong phyogs nas ji ltar bstan pa /
NK050(wi)002:71: tha mar chos dbyings snang stong zung du 'jug pa'i ye shes ji bzhin par bstan pa'i tshul lo //
NK050(wi)002:73: 'on kyang gang zag blo dman pa rnams la sogs /
NK050(wi)002:76: zhar byung stong nyid don spyi'i tshul du bsgom pa'i tshul gnyis /
NK050(wi)002:78: bar par rnam thar gsum ldan sogs /
NK050(wi)002:80: de yang chos nyid kyi sogs /
NK050(wi)002:82: de ltar byang sems blo che ba sogs /
NK050(wi)002:84: des na snying po'i rang bzhin sogs /
NK050(wi)002:87: gnyis pa sngags dang mtshams sbyor tshul la /
NK050(wi)002:89: mdo las sngags khyad par du 'phags pa'i gnad bshad pa gnyis las /
NK050(wi)002:91: des na chos dbyings 'od gsal lam sogs /
NK050(wi)002:94: gsum pa theg chen bla med kyi rigs khams ngos bzung ba la /
NK050(wi)002:96: de yod par rtags kyis nges tshul /
NK050(wi)002:97: de las 'bras bu sku gsum 'grub tshul /
NK050(wi)002:98: de la gzhan lugs dgag pa /
NK050(wi)002:99: rang lugs rnam par dag pa'i phyogs bzhag pa dang lnga las /
NK050(wi)002:101: de lta bu'i bla na med pa'am sogs /
NK050(wi)002:103: de lta bu'i rang bzhin gnas rigs sogs /
NK050(wi)002:105: des na rgyu rigs de gnyis sogs /
NK050(wi)002:107: de ltar ma shes par sogs /
NK050(wi)002:110: de grub mtha' gzhan gyi'ang dgongs pa'i zhe phug yin par bstan pa /
NK050(wi)002:111: zhar byung dbu ma rnam gnyis kyi dgongs pa mi 'gal bar sgrub pa gsum las /
NK050(wi)002:113: des na rigs gnyis kyang sogs /
NK050(wi)002:115: de dang mthun par 'gro ba'i mgon po sogs /
NK050(wi)002:116: gsum pa de'i phyir tshig spyi sbas sogs /
NK050(wi)002:117: bzhi pa bden gnyis kyi rang bzhin bstan pa la /
NK050(wi)002:118: don dam dang dbyer med tshul dang /
NK050(wi)002:119: tha snyad du ji ltar dbye ba'i tshul bstan pa gnyis las /
NK050(wi)002:121: des na snang stong gang rung re'i sogs /
NK050(wi)002:126: 'di la tha snyad pa'i kun tu tshad ma sogs /
NK050(wi)002:128: rang byung gi ye shes rtag par sgrub pa /
NK050(wi)002:130: de la gzhan gyi log rtog bzlog pa dang gsum las /
NK050(wi)002:132: des na gnas snang mthun par gyur pa'i nye sogs /
NK050(wi)002:134: der ma zad chos nyid rang bzhin gyi sogs /
NK050(wi)002:136: 'o na sangs rgyas kyis phung sogs so //
NK050(wi)002:137: gnyis pa lam nyams su len tshul dngos la gnyis /
NK050(wi)002:138: mdo sngags kyi lam nyams su len tshul gyi dbye ba spyir bstan /
NK050(wi)002:139: bye brag rdo rje theg pa'i lam nyams su len tshul rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK050(wi)002:141: de ltar legs par gtan la phebs nas sogs /
NK050(wi)002:142: gnyis pa la sngags phyi nang gnyis las /
NK050(wi)002:146: sngags phyi pa las khyad par du 'phags pa'i tshul gyis mdor bstan /
NK050(wi)002:147: nang pa gsum gyi khyad par rgyas par bshad /
NK050(wi)002:148: gsum ka'i gnad bsdus te la shan 'byed pa'i tshul dang gsum las /
NK050(wi)002:149: dang po thabs kyi theg pa'am nang rgyud sogs /
NK050(wi)002:155: de la'ang bskyed rdzogs rnam pa gsum gyi bskyed pa ma h+aa sogs /
NK050(wi)002:157: rdzogs pa a nu yo gas sogs /
NK050(wi)002:159: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo gas sogs /
NK050(wi)002:160: gsum pa gnad bsdus te la shan 'byed pa ni /
NK050(wi)002:161: mdor na 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad sogs so //
NK050(wi)002:162: gsum pa mthar phyin 'bras bu bstan pa ni /
NK050(wi)002:163: des na rang bzhin gnas rigs gdod ma'i 'od gsal sogs so //
NK050(wi)002:164: rtsa ba'i gsum pa mjug gi don la /
NK050(wi)002:165: gzhung don snying por dril nas gdams pa /
NK050(wi)002:166: de ltar rtogs pa'i dgos ched dam phan yon /
NK050(wi)002:167: rtsom pa mthar phyin nas nongs pa bshags shing dge ba bsngo ba /
NK050(wi)002:168: byed pa po'i ming dang gnas smos pa bzhi las /
NK050(wi)002:170: des na sangs rgyas dang sems can sogs /
NK050(wi)002:175: gdod ma'i 'od gsal bde gshegs snying po ni sogs /
NK050(wi)002:178: thog mar gang dran 'phral bris par //
NK050(wi)002:179: slad nas sa bcad 'di ltar mthong //
NK050(wi)002:180: mchog sprul dam pa'i bzhed skong du //
